<h2 class="text-3xl">This site is a starting point</h2>

<p>You can take this template and create whatever you want. There are some useful snippets of HTML and great features built right in.
Modifying it to fit a brochure site is as simple as copying over your assets and copy.</p>

<h2 class="text-3xl">Features</h2>

<div class="features sm:flex sm:justify-around">
{%- for feature in features -%}
  <div class="border rounded border-yellow-600 sm:w-1/3 m-4 p-2">
    <p class="text-center font-semibold">{{ feature.title }}</p>
    <p>{{ feature.details }}</p>
    {# <time datetime="{{ page.date }}">{{ page.date | dateDisplay("LLLL d, y") }}</time> #}
  </div>
{%- endfor -%}
</div>